{"type":"message","id":"eed70288","parentId":"227afdb1","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:37:22.419Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要订一个明天 10 点半的会议提醒。我需要使用 cron 来设置一个定时提醒。\n\n首先，我需要确定明天的日期。当前是 2026-04-01，所以明天是 2026-04-02 10:30。\n\n我可以使用 openclaw 的 cron 功能来创建一个定时任务。让我检查一下 openclaw 是否有相关的命令。\n\n根据 OpenClaw 文档，我可以使用 `openclaw cron` 命令来管理定时任务。\n\n创建一个 cron 任务来在明天 10:30 发送提醒。\n\n让我先搜索一下 OpenClaw 的 cron 命令用法。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_40631143eb3b47649c012c4f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron --help"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":184,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":13424,"totalTokens":13614,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00005152,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00005218}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775025438636,"responseId":"msg_40055d1e-8b07-467f-88e1-e6dc8c70680d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"175e453b","parentId":"eed70288","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:37:25.465Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_40631143eb3b47649c012c4f","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.24 (cff6dc9) — Running on your hardware, reading your logs, judging nothing (mostly).\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3038,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.24 (cff6dc9) — Running on your hardware, reading your logs, judging nothing (mostly).\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage.","cwd":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-openclaw_ai"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775025445464}}
{"type":"message","id":"628fa6ba","parentId":"175e453b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:37:26.753Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我查看一下 `openclaw cron add` 的具体用法。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_c81262c61c424a3eb125b443","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add --help"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":50,"cacheRead":13424,"cacheWrite":399,"totalTokens":13879,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.000014000000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000014660000000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775025445465,"responseId":"msg_59d40bd9-1e0d-4736-af77-cd17f42d32a2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e1ede595","parentId":"628fa6ba","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:37:28.470Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_c81262c61c424a3eb125b443","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.24 (cff6dc9) — Finally, a use for that always-on Mac Mini under your desk.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron add|create [options]\n\nAdd a cron job\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id for delivery (multi-account setups)\n  --agent <id>           Agent id for this job\n  --announce             Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style) (default:\n                         false)\n  --at <when>            Run once at time (ISO with offset, or +duration). Use\n                         --tz for offset-less datetimes\n  --best-effort-deliver  Do not fail the job if delivery fails (default: false)\n  --channel <channel>    Delivery channel (last) (default: \"last\")\n  --cron <expr>          Cron expression (5-field or 6-field with seconds)\n  --delete-after-run     Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --deliver              Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to a\n                         chat.\n  --description <text>   Optional description\n  --disabled             Create job disabled (default: false)\n  --every <duration>     Run every duration (e.g. 10m, 1h)\n  --exact                Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0) (default:\n                         false)\n  --expect-final         Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output JSON (default: false)\n  --keep-after-run       Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --light-context        Use lightweight bootstrap context for agent jobs\n                         (default: false)\n  --message <text>       Agent message payload\n  --model <model>        Model override for agent jobs (provider/model or alias)\n  --name <name>          Job name\n  --no-deliver           Disable announce delivery and skip main-session summary\n  --session <target>     Session target (main|isolated)\n  --session-key <key>    Session key for job routing (e.g.\n                         agent:my-agent:my-session)\n  --stagger <duration>   Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\n  --system-event <text>  System event payload (main session)\n  --thinking <level>     Thinking level for agent jobs\n                         (off|minimal|low|medium|high|xhigh)\n  --timeout <ms>         Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\n  --timeout-seconds <n>  Timeout seconds for agent jobs\n  --to <dest>            Delivery destination (E.164, Telegram chatId, or\n                         Discord channel/user)\n  --token <token>        Gateway token (if required)\n  --tz <iana>            Timezone for cron expressions (IANA) (default: \"\")\n  --url <url>            Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to gateway.remote.url\n                         when configured)\n  --wake <mode>          Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat) (default: \"now\")"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1713,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.24 (cff6dc9) — Finally, a use for that always-on Mac Mini under your desk.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron add|create [options]\n\nAdd a cron job\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id for delivery (multi-account setups)\n  --agent <id>           Agent id for this job\n  --announce             Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style) (default:\n                         false)\n  --at <when>            Run once at time (ISO with offset, or +duration). Use\n                         --tz for offset-less datetimes\n  --best-effort-deliver  Do not fail the job if delivery fails (default: false)\n  --channel <channel>    Delivery channel (last) (default: \"last\")\n  --cron <expr>          Cron expression (5-field or 6-field with seconds)\n  --delete-after-run     Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --deliver              Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to a\n                         chat.\n  --description <text>   Optional description\n  --disabled             Create job disabled (default: false)\n  --every <duration>     Run every duration (e.g. 10m, 1h)\n  --exact                Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0) (default:\n                         false)\n  --expect-final         Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output JSON (default: false)\n  --keep-after-run       Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --light-context        Use lightweight bootstrap context for agent jobs\n                         (default: false)\n  --message <text>       Agent message payload\n  --model <model>        Model override for agent jobs (provider/model or alias)\n  --name <name>          Job name\n  --no-deliver           Disable announce delivery and skip main-session summary\n  --session <target>     Session target (main|isolated)\n  --session-key <key>    Session key for job routing (e.g.\n                         agent:my-agent:my-session)\n  --stagger <duration>   Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\n  --system-event <text>  System event payload (main session)\n  --thinking <level>     Thinking level for agent jobs\n                         (off|minimal|low|medium|high|xhigh)\n  --timeout <ms>         Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\n  --timeout-seconds <n>  Timeout seconds for agent jobs\n  --to <dest>            Delivery destination (E.164, Telegram chatId, or\n                         Discord channel/user)\n  --token <token>        Gateway token (if required)\n  --tz <iana>            Timezone for cron expressions (IANA) (default: \"\")\n  --url <url>            Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to gateway.remote.url\n                         when configured)\n  --wake <mode>          Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat) (default: \"now\")","cwd":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-openclaw_ai"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775025448470}}
