{"type":"message","id":"a22c31cb","parentId":"6a3e34ba","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:37:40.270Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]\n✅ 已设置会议提醒：\n\n- **时间**：明天（4 月 2 日）10:30\n- **任务 ID**：`05bc1e59-2b48-46b3-8a9a-0b217e11626b`\n- **提醒内容**：⏰ 会议提醒：您有一个会议在 10:30 开始\n\n提醒会在指定时间自动发送给你，完成后会自动删除。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":121,"cacheRead":14592,"cacheWrite":795,"totalTokens":15514,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00003388,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00003454}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775025454831,"responseId":"msg_f39ecdf8-12bc-410f-b9fc-17cc95f56567"}}
