{"type":"message","id":"2934a7bb","parentId":"79c4ba42","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:43:55.931Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想让我帮他安装飞书官方 CLI。根据搜索结果，安装步骤是：\n\n1. 通过 npm 安装 CLI\n2. 安装 CLI SKILL\n3. 配置应用凭证\n4. 登录授权\n\n让我先检查一下用户是否已经安装了 npm/node，然后执行安装命令。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_df45d159cd9c4b3e9253ac2a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"npm install -g @larksuite/cli"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":101,"cacheRead":34181,"cacheWrite":7233,"totalTokens":41521,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00002828,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00002894}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775025833655,"responseId":"msg_a199d6b3-62b0-4448-a520-e528268f589a"}}
