{"type":"message","id":"a38920ef","parentId":"ac647686","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:44:58.761Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"CLI 和 SKILL 都安装成功了！现在需要配置认证。根据文档，下一步是：\n1. `lark-cli config init` - 配置应用凭证\n2. `lark-cli auth login --recommend` - 登录授权\n\n但是这些是交互式命令，需要用户参与。让我先检查一下 lark-cli 是否安装成功，然后告诉用户下一步需要做什么。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"CLI 和 SKILL 都安装成功了！现在需要配置认证。让我先验证一下安装：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_644f397e99474d939fb9d6bc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"lark-cli --version"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":137,"cacheRead":41910,"cacheWrite":3336,"totalTokens":45389,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.000038360000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00003902}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775025896153,"responseId":"msg_b59c90d7-b41b-45e7-80da-901958dab7b7"}}
