{"type":"message","id":"b6bf8ce2","parentId":"fb3f02fd","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:45:02.776Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"安装完成！现在需要配置认证。根据文档，配置认证是交互式的，需要用户自己操作。让我告诉用户后续步骤。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]\n✅ **飞书官方 CLI 安装成功！**\n\n## 已安装\n- **lark-cli** v1.0.1\n- **19 个 AI Agent Skills**（包括 lark-calendar、lark-doc、lark-im 等）\n- Skills 已链接到 OpenClaw 和 Claude Code\n\n## 下一步：配置认证 ⚠️\n\n认证需要**交互式操作**，需要你手动完成：\n\n```bash\n# 1. 配置应用凭证（仅需一次）\nlark-cli config init\n\n# 2. 登录授权（自动选择常用权限）\nlark-cli auth login --recommend\n```\n\n## 认证后会话\n完成认证后，你就可以：\n\n```bash\n# 查看日程\nlark-cli calendar +agenda\n\n# 创建明天 10:30 的会议\nlark-cli calendar create-event \\\n  --summary \"会议\" \\\n  --start \"2026-04-02T10:30:00+08:00\" \\\n  --end \"2026-04-02T11:30:00+08:00\"\n\n# 让我帮你操作\n你：\"帮我创建一个明天 10 点半的会议\"\n```\n\n需要我现在帮你启动配置流程吗？会弹出浏览器让你授权。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":335,"cacheRead":45246,"cacheWrite":161,"totalTokens":45748,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.0000938,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00009446}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775025898849,"responseId":"msg_2ee307af-5acc-4c85-87d8-18dc4d9090a7"}}
