{"type":"message","id":"2e1d4856","parentId":"f2e88539","timestamp":"2026-04-01T07:04:12.027Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想让我用 lark-calendar 技能创建日程，晚上 6 点，地点在\"白洞\"。\n\n但是我需要先确认：\n1. 飞书 CLI 是否已经完成认证？之前用户没有完成认证流程\n2. 我需要检查 lark-cli 是否已经配置好\n\n让我先尝试运行一个命令看看认证状态，然后再创建日程。\n\n首先，我需要确定日期和时间：\n- \"晚上 6 点\" = 18:00\n- 日期应该是今天（2026-04-01）\n- 需要设置结束时间，假设会议 1 小时，那就是 19:00 结束\n\n让我先检查一下认证状态，然后尝试创建日程。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_9d4ecf2257ba4d3ca79d2991","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"lark-cli calendar create-event --summary \"白洞会议\" --start \"2026-04-01T18:00:00+08:00\" --end \"2026-04-01T19:00:00+08:00\" --location \"白洞\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":261,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":49451,"totalTokens":49718,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00007308,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00007374}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775027044878,"responseId":"msg_3725c293-f71a-4b63-9846-eff34faac63c"}}
