{"type":"message","id":"bc3ec352","parentId":"7383c2e2","timestamp":"2026-04-01T07:04:21.007Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我等待用户批准，先检查一下之前的配置会话是否还运行着。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]\n需要你先批准这个命令 🔐\n\n飞书 CLI 还没有完成认证，但我可以先尝试执行命令。系统要求批准：\n\n**请回复以下命令批准：**\n```\n/approve 5effaaa8 allow-once\n```\n\n或者如果以后还想让我帮你操作飞书 CLI：\n```\n/approve 5effaaa8 allow-always\n```\n\n---\n\n**⚠️ 注意：** 飞书 CLI 可能还没完成认证（之前那个配置链接你没点完），执行可能会失败。\n\n如果失败，你需要：\n1. 先打开之前的链接完成认证：`https://open.feishu.cn/page/cli?user_code=EE26-6VVG&lpv=1.0.1&ocv=1.0.1&from=cli`\n2. 然后我再帮你创建日程\n\n你想先完成认证，还是直接批准命令试试看？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":217,"cacheRead":49939,"cacheWrite":109,"totalTokens":50271,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00006076,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00006142}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775027057255,"responseId":"msg_f977e213-3e8b-4e69-a87d-9d4cb677569d"}}
