{"type":"message","id":"6e7f6936","parentId":"eb9935e0","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:12:25.314Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"检查登录状态也需要批准。看起来用户需要批准每个命令。让我告诉用户这个情况，并建议他们使用 allow-always 来减少频繁的批准请求。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]\n**还没登录** ❌\n\n每个命令都需要你批准，有点麻烦 😅\n\n**建议：** 用 `allow-always` 批准一次，以后就不用每次都点了：\n\n```\n/approve 235fa12a allow-always\n```\n\n这样可以批准 clawhub 相关的所有命令。\n\n---\n\n**或者** 你也可以直接在 clawhub.com 上手动安装技能：\n1. 访问 https://clawhub.ai\n2. 搜索 \"github\" 相关技能\n3. 复制技能名称\n4. 让我执行 `clawhub install <skill-name>`\n\n你想怎么弄？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":176,"cacheRead":54319,"cacheWrite":327,"totalTokens":54828,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00004928,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00004994}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775031141888,"responseId":"msg_4bedf599-4a42-4cf5-bcd9-f342eab61ecb"}}
