{"type":"message","id":"a08a4851","parentId":"1abc2b46","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:22:05.517Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要检查他的 memory 向量检索是否正常。这涉及到 OpenClaw 的 memory 功能。\n\nOpenClaw 有 memory 搜索功能，可能是基于向量检索的。让我先检查一下 memory 相关的配置和状态。\n\n根据之前看到的插件列表，有：\n- Memory (Core) - memory-core - 已加载\n- memory-lancedb - 已禁用（LanceDB 支持的长期记忆插件）\n\n如果用户想要向量检索，可能需要启用 memory-lancedb 插件。\n\n让我先检查 memory 的状态和配置。我需要执行一些命令来检查：\n1. `openclaw memory` 相关的命令\n2. 或者检查配置文件\n\n让我先查看 openclaw memory 的命令帮助。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"帮你检查 memory 向量检索的配置和状态：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_6f5267b5006b481fbb2bff9a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw memory --help"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":200,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":55103,"totalTokens":55309,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.000056000000000000006,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00005666}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775031714365,"responseId":"msg_0cd860f0-52e8-4587-9f9a-608cb06ef88b"}}
