{"type":"message","id":"0a320fe0","parentId":"b2784395","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:22:08.264Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Need to ask user for approval.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]\n需要批准 🔐\n\n```\n/approve ff71b0da allow-once\n```\n\n---\n\n**关于 Memory 向量检索：**\n\nOpenClaw 有两种 memory 模式：\n\n1. **Memory (Core)** ✅ 已加载\n   - 基于文件搜索（全文检索）\n   - 不是向量检索\n\n2. **memory-lancedb** ❌ 已禁用\n   - 基于 LanceDB 的向量检索\n   - 支持语义搜索、自动捕获\n\n如果你想要**向量检索**，需要启用 `memory-lancedb` 插件。\n\n批准命令后我帮你：\n1. 检查当前 memory 状态\n2. 确认是否需要启用向量检索\n3. 如果需要，帮你配置 LanceDB\n\n要批准吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":182,"cacheRead":55103,"cacheWrite":357,"totalTokens":55648,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00005096000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000051620000000000004}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775031725558,"responseId":"msg_cc3ea487-35b3-4f72-8ca7-73150b9b39b8"}}
