{"type":"message","id":"3df279e9","parentId":"28971e16","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:31:56.893Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要配置千问的嵌入模型，并提供了 API key。我需要帮用户配置 OpenClaw 的 memory 嵌入模型。\n\n根据之前的信息，用户想要用\"千问的 v4\"嵌入模型。千问是阿里云的模型，对应的 provider 应该是 DashScope（阿里灵积）。\n\n在 OpenClaw 中，配置模型通常通过 `openclaw config` 或 `openclaw models` 命令。\n\n让我先查看一下如何配置 memory 的嵌入模型。可能需要：\n1. 配置 provider（DashScope/aliyun）\n2. 设置 API key\n3. 指定嵌入模型\n4. 然后重新索引\n\nAPI key: sk-a2675c4123764e46880426a87bff42de\n\n我需要小心处理这个 API key，不要在不必要的地方暴露它。\n\n让我先查看 openclaw config 或 openclaw memory 相关的配置命令。\n\n根据 OpenClaw 的文档，配置 memory 嵌入模型可能需要：\n1. `openclaw config set memory.embedding.model <model>`\n2. `openclaw config set memory.embedding.provider <provider>`\n3. 或者通过 `openclaw models` 命令配置\n\n让我先尝试查看配置选项。\n\n另外，API key 需要安全地存储，通常是通过 `openclaw config set` 或者环境变量。\n\n让我尝试执行配置命令。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"好的！帮你配置千问嵌入模型。千问是阿里云 DashScope 的模型，我来帮你设置。\n\n先配置 API key 和模型：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_a859986bd01a4e1bbf73aa4d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw config set memory.embedding.provider dashscope"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":382,"cacheRead":56851,"cacheWrite":2016,"totalTokens":59255,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00010696,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00010762}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775032308560,"responseId":"msg_364841fe-fa60-41a7-82e1-cfe8d14e6abb"}}
