{"type":"message","id":"2fef2a31","parentId":"3f0a17cf","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:33:12.105Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我想想另一种方法。用户想要配置千问的嵌入模型来做向量检索。OpenClaw 的配置结构比较复杂，API key 不能直接放在配置文件中。\n\n从之前的 `openclaw memory status` 输出看到：\n- `Provider: none (requested: auto)`\n\n这说明系统尝试自动检测 provider 但失败了。\n\n让我尝试使用 `openclaw models` 命令来发现和配置嵌入模型，或者查看是否有其他方式配置。\n\n实际上，我可能可以直接使用 `openclaw config set` 命令来配置，但需要使用正确的路径。让我想想 OpenClaw 的配置结构...\n\n从配置文件来看，auth profiles 只是声明了 provider 的模式，实际的 API key 可能通过以下方式配置：\n1. 环境变量（如 DASHSCOPE_API_KEY）\n2. 系统密钥链\n3. secrets 插件\n\n让我尝试使用 `openclaw config set` 命令配置 secrets，或者查看是否有专门的地方配置 API key。\n\n另外，我也注意到 `custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com` provider 已经在使用了（用于 qwen3.5-plus 聊天模型），这意味着 API key 可能已经配置过了，只是通过某种外部方式（如环境变量）。\n\n如果 DashScope 的 API key 已经配置了（因为聊天模型能正常工作），那么我只需要添加嵌入模型的定义。\n\n让我尝试另一种方式：直接在 models.providers.custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com.models 中添加嵌入模型，但不使用 `type` 和 `dimension` 这些不被识别的字段。\n\n或者，我可以查看 OpenClaw 文档，了解嵌入模型的正确配置格式。\n\n让我尝试使用 web_search 搜索 OpenClaw 嵌入模型配置。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"让我搜索一下 OpenClaw 如何配置嵌入模型：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_64d2bf1358654abab6d2fde0","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":5,"query":"OpenClaw memory embedding model config 配置"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":420,"cacheRead":67733,"cacheWrite":136,"totalTokens":68295,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00011760000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00011826000000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775032386116,"responseId":"msg_e6cead1b-c50c-4767-b682-998a00f3a496"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d82f8c52","parentId":"2fef2a31","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:33:18.259Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_64d2bf1358654abab6d2fde0","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"OpenClaw memory embedding model config 配置\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 6120,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"06ad27802149684b\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nMemory configuration reference - OpenClaw\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"06ad27802149684b\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/reference/memory-config\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e221c08c7850f9f8\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n# Pick the same state dir OpenClaw uses STATE_DIR=&quot;${OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR:-$HOME/.openclaw}&quot; export XDG_CONFIG_HOME=&quot;$STATE_DIR/agents/main/qmd/xdg-config&quot; export XDG_CACHE_HOME=&quot;$STATE_DIR/agents/main/qmd/xdg-cache&quot; # (Optional) force an index refresh + embeddings qmd update qmd embed # Warm up / trigger first-time model downloads qmd query &quot;test&quot; -c memory-root --json &gt;/dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e221c08c7850f9f8\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"5 days ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"docs.openclaw.ai\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e4d3e6d8da517e47\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nOpenClaw Memory Configuration — Embeddings, Context Pruning & Compaction Guide | MoltFounders\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e4d3e6d8da517e47\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://moltfounders.com/openclaw-runbook/memory-configuration\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bed8e334073ed6c0\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHere&#x27;s how all three pieces fit together in your openclaw.json: ... { &quot;memorySearch&quot;: { &quot;sources&quot;: [&quot;memory&quot;, &quot;sessions&quot;], &quot;experimental&quot;: { &quot;sessionMemory&quot;: true }, &quot;provider&quot;: &quot;openai&quot;, &quot;model&quot;: &quot;text-embedding-3-small&quot; }, &quot;contextPruning&quot;: { &quot;mode&quot;: &quot;cache-ttl&quot;, &quot;ttl&quot;: &quot;6h&quot;, &quot;keepLastAssistants&quot;: 3 }, &quot;compaction&quot;: { &quot;mode&quot;: &quot;default&quot;, &quot;memoryFlush&quot;: { &quot;enabled&quot;: true, &quot;softThresholdTokens&quot;: 40000, &quot;prompt&quot;: &quot;Distill this session to memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bed8e334073ed6c0\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"February 10, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"moltfounders.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"fa1c9551b9b335eb\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGitHub - abhpc/openclaw-mem0: Long-term memory plugin for OpenClaw agents, powered by Mem0. Self-hosted with any OpenAI-compatible provider. · GitHub\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"fa1c9551b9b335eb\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/abhpc/openclaw-mem0/tree/main\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3e0c450dcc749cdf\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n{ &quot;plugins&quot;: { &quot;entries&quot;: { &quot;openclaw-mem0&quot;: { &quot;config&quot;: { &quot;mode&quot;: &quot;open-source&quot;, &quot;userId&quot;: &quot;default&quot;, &quot;autoCapture&quot;: true, &quot;autoRecall&quot;: true, &quot;oss&quot;: { &quot;embedder&quot;: { &quot;provider&quot;: &quot;openai&quot;, &quot;config&quot;: { &quot;apiKey&quot;: &quot;${YOUR_EMBEDDING_API_KEY}&quot;, &quot;baseURL&quot;: &quot;${YOUR_EMBEDDING_BASE_URL}&quot;, &quot;model&quot;: &quot;${YOUR_EMBEDDING_MODEL}&quot; } }, &quot;vectorStore&quot;: { &quot;provider&quot;: &quot;qdrant&quot;, &quot;config&quot;: { &quot;host&quot;: &quot;${QDRANT_HOST}&quot;, &quot;port&quot;: ${QDRANT_PORT}, &quot;collectionName&quot;: &quot;${COLLECTION_NAME}&quot; } }, &quot;llm&quot;: { &quot;provider&quot;: &quot;openai&quot;, &quot;config&quot;: { &quot;apiKey&quot;: &quot;${YOUR_CHAT_API_KEY}&quot;, &quot;baseURL&quot;: &quot;${YOUR_CHAT_BASE_URL}&quot;, &quot;model&quot;: &quot;${YOUR_CHAT_MODEL}&quot; } } } } } } } }\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3e0c450dcc749cdf\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"github.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a5dc4a00fa0eaeef\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGitHub - MaydayV/openclaw-local-memory: OpenClaw 本地记忆系统配置指南 - 使用 Ollama + Qwen3 Embedding 实现完全本地化的语义搜索 · GitHub\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a5dc4a00fa0eaeef\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/MaydayV/openclaw-local-memory\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"98d77658df961303\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nopenclaw memory index --force · 验证搜索： 测试几个搜索查询，确保结果正常。 · 如果你之前使用云端 API（如 OpenAI Embeddings），迁移到本地： · 安装 Ollama 和 Qwen3（见上文） · 更新配置： · memorySearch: { enabled: true, provider: &quot;ollama&quot;, // 从 &quot;openai&quot; 改为 &quot;ollama&quot; model: &quot;qwen3-embedding:0.6b&quot;, // 删除 apiKey 配置 } 重建索引： ·\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"98d77658df961303\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"github.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c3eac318a4e652fd\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nMemory - OpenClaw Docs | Learn OpenClaw\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c3eac318a4e652fd\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.learnclawdbot.org/docs/concepts/memory\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3073957de0bb94d8\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nIf the sqlite-vec extension is missing or fails to load, OpenClaw logs the error and continues with the JS fallback (no vector table). extensionPath overrides the bundled sqlite-vec path (useful for custom builds or non-standard install locations). Default local embedding model: hf:ggml-org/embeddinggemma-300M-GGUF/embeddinggemma-300M-Q8_0.gguf (~0.6 GB). When memorySearch.provider = &quot;local&quot;, node-llama-cpp resolves modelPath; if the GGUF is missing it auto-downloads to the cache (or local.modelCacheDir if set), then loads it.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3073957de0bb94d8\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.learnclawdbot.org\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"OpenClaw memory embedding model config 配置","provider":"brave","count":5,"tookMs":6120,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"brave","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"06ad27802149684b\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nMemory configuration reference - OpenClaw\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"06ad27802149684b\">>>","url":"https://docs.openclaw.ai/reference/memory-config","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"e221c08c7850f9f8\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n# Pick the same state dir OpenClaw uses STATE_DIR=&quot;${OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR:-$HOME/.openclaw}&quot; export XDG_CONFIG_HOME=&quot;$STATE_DIR/agents/main/qmd/xdg-config&quot; export XDG_CACHE_HOME=&quot;$STATE_DIR/agents/main/qmd/xdg-cache&quot; # (Optional) force an index refresh + embeddings qmd update qmd embed # Warm up / trigger first-time model downloads qmd query &quot;test&quot; -c memory-root --json &gt;/dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"e221c08c7850f9f8\">>>","published":"5 days ago","siteName":"docs.openclaw.ai"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"e4d3e6d8da517e47\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nOpenClaw Memory Configuration — Embeddings, Context Pruning & Compaction Guide | MoltFounders\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"e4d3e6d8da517e47\">>>","url":"https://moltfounders.com/openclaw-runbook/memory-configuration","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"bed8e334073ed6c0\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHere&#x27;s how all three pieces fit together in your openclaw.json: ... { &quot;memorySearch&quot;: { &quot;sources&quot;: [&quot;memory&quot;, &quot;sessions&quot;], &quot;experimental&quot;: { &quot;sessionMemory&quot;: true }, &quot;provider&quot;: &quot;openai&quot;, &quot;model&quot;: &quot;text-embedding-3-small&quot; }, &quot;contextPruning&quot;: { &quot;mode&quot;: &quot;cache-ttl&quot;, &quot;ttl&quot;: &quot;6h&quot;, &quot;keepLastAssistants&quot;: 3 }, &quot;compaction&quot;: { &quot;mode&quot;: &quot;default&quot;, &quot;memoryFlush&quot;: { &quot;enabled&quot;: true, &quot;softThresholdTokens&quot;: 40000, &quot;prompt&quot;: &quot;Distill this session to memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"bed8e334073ed6c0\">>>","published":"February 10, 2026","siteName":"moltfounders.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"fa1c9551b9b335eb\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nGitHub - abhpc/openclaw-mem0: Long-term memory plugin for OpenClaw agents, powered by Mem0. Self-hosted with any OpenAI-compatible provider. · GitHub\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"fa1c9551b9b335eb\">>>","url":"https://github.com/abhpc/openclaw-mem0/tree/main","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3e0c450dcc749cdf\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n{ &quot;plugins&quot;: { &quot;entries&quot;: { &quot;openclaw-mem0&quot;: { &quot;config&quot;: { &quot;mode&quot;: &quot;open-source&quot;, &quot;userId&quot;: &quot;default&quot;, &quot;autoCapture&quot;: true, &quot;autoRecall&quot;: true, &quot;oss&quot;: { &quot;embedder&quot;: { &quot;provider&quot;: &quot;openai&quot;, &quot;config&quot;: { &quot;apiKey&quot;: &quot;${YOUR_EMBEDDING_API_KEY}&quot;, &quot;baseURL&quot;: &quot;${YOUR_EMBEDDING_BASE_URL}&quot;, &quot;model&quot;: &quot;${YOUR_EMBEDDING_MODEL}&quot; } }, &quot;vectorStore&quot;: { &quot;provider&quot;: &quot;qdrant&quot;, &quot;config&quot;: { &quot;host&quot;: &quot;${QDRANT_HOST}&quot;, &quot;port&quot;: ${QDRANT_PORT}, &quot;collectionName&quot;: &quot;${COLLECTION_NAME}&quot; } }, &quot;llm&quot;: { &quot;provider&quot;: &quot;openai&quot;, &quot;config&quot;: { &quot;apiKey&quot;: &quot;${YOUR_CHAT_API_KEY}&quot;, &quot;baseURL&quot;: &quot;${YOUR_CHAT_BASE_URL}&quot;, &quot;model&quot;: &quot;${YOUR_CHAT_MODEL}&quot; } } } } } } } }\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3e0c450dcc749cdf\">>>","siteName":"github.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a5dc4a00fa0eaeef\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nGitHub - MaydayV/openclaw-local-memory: OpenClaw 本地记忆系统配置指南 - 使用 Ollama + Qwen3 Embedding 实现完全本地化的语义搜索 · GitHub\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a5dc4a00fa0eaeef\">>>","url":"https://github.com/MaydayV/openclaw-local-memory","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"98d77658df961303\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nopenclaw memory index --force · 验证搜索： 测试几个搜索查询，确保结果正常。 · 如果你之前使用云端 API（如 OpenAI Embeddings），迁移到本地： · 安装 Ollama 和 Qwen3（见上文） · 更新配置： · memorySearch: { enabled: true, provider: &quot;ollama&quot;, // 从 &quot;openai&quot; 改为 &quot;ollama&quot; model: &quot;qwen3-embedding:0.6b&quot;, // 删除 apiKey 配置 } 重建索引： ·\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"98d77658df961303\">>>","siteName":"github.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c3eac318a4e652fd\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nMemory - OpenClaw Docs | Learn OpenClaw\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c3eac318a4e652fd\">>>","url":"https://www.learnclawdbot.org/docs/concepts/memory","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3073957de0bb94d8\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nIf the sqlite-vec extension is missing or fails to load, OpenClaw logs the error and continues with the JS fallback (no vector table). extensionPath overrides the bundled sqlite-vec path (useful for custom builds or non-standard install locations). Default local embedding model: hf:ggml-org/embeddinggemma-300M-GGUF/embeddinggemma-300M-Q8_0.gguf (~0.6 GB). When memorySearch.provider = &quot;local&quot;, node-llama-cpp resolves modelPath; if the GGUF is missing it auto-downloads to the cache (or local.modelCacheDir if set), then loads it.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3073957de0bb94d8\">>>","siteName":"www.learnclawdbot.org"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775032398238}}
{"type":"message","id":"a978c74e","parentId":"d82f8c52","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:33:25.437Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"从搜索结果中，我找到了有用的信息！根据 OpenClaw 文档，memory 配置应该在 `openclaw.json` 的顶层，使用 `memorySearch` 配置项。\n\n从 moltfounders.com 的文档看到：\n```json\n{\n  \"memorySearch\": {\n    \"sources\": [\"memory\", \"sessions\"],\n    \"provider\": \"openai\",\n    \"model\": \"text-embedding-3-small\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n所以我需要在 `openclaw.json` 中添加 `memorySearch` 配置项，指定 provider 和 model。\n\n对于 DashScope/千问的嵌入模型，provider 应该是 `custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com`，模型是 `text-embedding-v3`。\n\n让我添加这个配置：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_20762aa06f7d4186b3289cc2","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"  \"plugins\": {\n    \"allow\": [\n      \"memory-core\",\n      \"feishu\",\n      \"browser\"\n    ],\n    \"slots\": {\n      \"memory\": \"memory-core\"\n    },\n    \"entries\": {\n      \"feishu\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      },\n      \"memory-core\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      },\n      \"brave\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"config\": {\n          \"webSearch\": {\n            \"apiKey\": \"BSApNLzPP62GcVo0A2hYdIzZDrpXD_3\"\n          }\n        }\n      },\n      \"browser\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      }\n    },\n    \"installs\": {}\n  },\n  \"memorySearch\": {\n    \"sources\": [\"memory\"],\n    \"provider\": \"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com\",\n    \"model\": \"text-embedding-v3\"\n  }\n}","oldText":"  \"plugins\": {\n    \"allow\": [\n      \"memory-core\",\n      \"feishu\",\n      \"browser\"\n    ],\n    \"slots\": {\n      \"memory\": \"memory-core\"\n    },\n    \"entries\": {\n      \"feishu\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      },\n      \"memory-core\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      },\n      \"brave\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"config\": {\n          \"webSearch\": {\n            \"apiKey\": \"BSApNLzPP62GcVo0A2hYdIzZDrpXD_3\"\n          }\n        }\n      },\n      \"browser\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      }\n    },\n    \"installs\": {}\n  }\n}"}],"file":"~/.openclaw/openclaw.json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":667,"cacheRead":67869,"cacheWrite":2555,"totalTokens":71097,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00018676,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00018742000000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775032398261,"responseId":"msg_fb173a46-f60c-460c-b7ff-71cfb4f0cd37"}}
