{"type":"message","id":"3f7b5775","parentId":"1a1eabe1","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:43:39.029Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问我配置好了没有。让我回顾一下我做了什么：\n\n1. 添加了 memorySearch 配置到 openclaw.json\n2. 配置验证通过了\n3. 尝试重启 gateway 但命令被中止了 (SIGTERM)\n\n现在我需要：\n1. 确认 gateway 是否重启成功\n2. 运行 memory index 来建立索引\n3. 检查 memory 状态确认向量检索是否正常工作\n\n让我先检查 gateway 状态，然后运行索引。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]\n**配置已添加，验证通过** ✅\n\n但还需要两步：\n\n1. **重启 gateway** - 刚才重启命令被中断了\n2. **重建索引** - 让向量检索生效\n\n让我继续完成：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_cd2adb8e7f524c4d8cac5965","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway status"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":188,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":71534,"totalTokens":71728,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.000052640000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000533}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775033006070,"responseId":"msg_0a5e97bf-b914-42cd-a6d8-f8d08c295629"}}
