{"type":"message","id":"35e8ec1b","parentId":"c5eb13e3","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:44:04.186Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问 3c86a5ee 是谁的 ID。这是我刚才请求批准的命令的 ID。让我解释清楚：\n\n- 3c86a5ee 是 approval ID\n- 对应的命令是 `systemctl --user restart openclaw-gateway`\n- 用于重启 OpenClaw gateway 服务\n\n用户可能对批准机制不太熟悉，我需要解释清楚。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]\n**3c86a5ee** 是刚才那个**重启 gateway 命令的批准 ID** 🔐\n\n```\n命令：systemctl --user restart openclaw-gateway\n批准 ID: 3c86a5ee\n完整 ID: 3c86a5ee-cfc3-44bf-b997-3b8321684b35\n```\n\n---\n\n## 批准机制说明\n\nOpenClaw 执行外部命令时需要你批准，防止恶意操作。每个待批准的命令都有一个短 ID。\n\n**批准格式：**\n```\n/approve 3c86a5ee allow-once\n```\n\n- `allow-once` — 只批准这一次\n- `allow-always` — 以后同类命令都自动批准（不用每次都问）\n\n---\n\n## 现在需要你做什么\n\n如果你想完成 memory 向量检索的配置，需要：\n\n1. **批准重启 gateway** — 加载新的 memory 配置\n2. **然后我运行索引** — 建立向量索引\n\n**回复：**\n```\n/approve 3c86a5ee allow-once\n```\n\n或者如果觉得每次都批准太烦：\n```\n/approve 3c86a5ee allow-always\n```\n\n不批准的话，配置无法生效，向量检索还是用不了。你决定！"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":383,"cacheRead":71534,"cacheWrite":1231,"totalTokens":73154,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00010724000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00010790000000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775033037872,"responseId":"msg_b6e808f5-f180-447a-9338-7cb8919f3b22"}}
