{"type":"message","id":"6323a5d5","parentId":"9d434852","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:56:37.109Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户批评我了，说我没有主动记东西。让我回顾一下 AGENTS.md 的要求：\n\n从 AGENTS.md 中：\n- **研究对话必须保存到记忆**：讨论 OpenClaw 框架知识、架构理解、配置要点时，主动写入 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- **不要等用户提醒**：每次有实质性学习内容时，立即保存\n- **每日总结**：一天结束时，确保当天的重要学习都已归档\n\n用户说得对！我们今天讨论了很多内容：\n1. 飞书 CLI 安装和配置\n2. lark-calendar 创建日程\n3. clawhub 技能安装\n4. Memory 向量检索配置\n5. OpenClaw 配置结构（memorySearch、provider、model 等）\n\n这些都是 OpenClaw 框架的重要知识，我应该主动保存到 `memory/2026-04-01.md`（今天的日期是 2026-04-01）。\n\n用户今天 2026-04-01，所以我应该写入 `memory/2026-04-01.md`。\n\n让我先创建这个文件，记录今天的学习内容。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"你说得对！我错了 😓\n\n今天聊了这么多 OpenClaw 的知识点，我应该主动保存的。让我现在补上：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_c8162c180f624abebf2a8857","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p ~/.openclaw/workspace-fox-openclaw_ai/memory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":324,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":73440,"totalTokens":73770,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00009072000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00009138000000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775033786686,"responseId":"msg_deecf38c-ef32-4da1-a44c-8b8213366b3a"}}
