{"type":"message","id":"3949e4cf","parentId":"871f7515","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:57:00.637Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Write tool succeeded! Now I should acknowledge that I've saved the memory and apologize for not doing it earlier. I should also remind the user about the memory vector search configuration that still needs to be completed.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]\n**已保存！抱歉之前没主动记** 🙏\n\n今天聊的所有 OpenClaw 知识点都写到 `memory/2026-04-01.md` 了，包括：\n\n1. ✅ 飞书 CLI 安装和认证流程\n2. ✅ Memory 向量检索配置步骤\n3. ✅ OpenClaw 配置结构要点\n4. ✅ ClawHub 技能管理\n5. ✅ 批准机制使用说明\n\n---\n\n**教训记住了：** 以后讨论 OpenClaw 框架知识时，**立即保存**，不等你提醒。\n\n---\n\n## 回来继续刚才的配置\n\nMemory 向量检索配置还差两步：\n\n1. **重启 gateway** — 需要批准：`/approve 3c86a5ee allow-once`\n2. **重建索引** — 重启后我执行\n\n要现在完成吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":239,"cacheRead":73941,"cacheWrite":1193,"totalTokens":75379,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00006692,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00006758}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775033812858,"responseId":"msg_fac90068-f5d0-4faf-bdc0-83e7d01c886d"}}
