{"type":"message","id":"03d1215b","parentId":"2ba15484","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:58:43.298Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我重建索引。我需要先重启 gateway 让配置生效，然后运行 memory index --force。\n\n重启 gateway 需要批准：`/approve 3c86a5ee allow-once`\n\n但用户没有直接批准，而是说\"重建下索引\"。可能用户以为我已经重启了 gateway，或者用户想让我直接运行索引命令。\n\n让我先尝试直接运行索引命令，看看是否需要重启 gateway。如果配置已经加载了，可能可以直接运行。\n\n但实际上，gateway 可能还没有重新加载配置，因为之前的重启命令被中断了，后来的重启命令需要批准但用户没有批准。\n\n让我先尝试运行索引命令，如果需要重启 gateway 会报错，到时候再请求批准。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]\n好，先尝试直接重建索引：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_8ce16d36f44143028703e2e9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw memory index --force"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":199,"cacheRead":75646,"cacheWrite":511,"totalTokens":76362,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00005572,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00005638}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775033919221,"responseId":"msg_e2922810-dadd-4595-80e9-218e6fb1f4a7"}}
