{"type":"message","id":"22065cf5","parentId":"a830b0e1","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:58:52.124Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"索引失败了，错误是 \"Unknown memory embedding provider: custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com\"。这说明：\n1. Gateway 没有重新加载配置（因为重启命令没执行）\n2. 或者 provider 名称不正确\n\n我需要：\n1. 先重启 gateway 让配置生效\n2. 或者检查 provider 名称是否正确\n\n让我先重启 gateway，然后再试。重启需要批准。\n\n但实际上，问题可能是 provider 名称。在 openclaw.json 中，provider 是 `custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com`，但嵌入模型的 provider 可能需要不同的名称或者需要额外配置。\n\n让我先尝试重启 gateway，看看是否能解决问题。如果还是失败，可能需要调整配置。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]\n**索引失败了** ❌\n\n错误：`Unknown memory embedding provider: custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com`\n\n原因：Gateway 还没重新加载配置。需要重启：\n\n**请批准重启：**\n```\n/approve 3c86a5ee allow-once\n```\n\n或者provider名称可能不对。让我先看看支持的provider有哪些：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_2fbb52c675474827b0113a2a","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":5,"query":"OpenClaw memory embedding provider dashscope aliyuncs 支持的provider"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":291,"cacheRead":76157,"cacheWrite":470,"totalTokens":76924,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00008148,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00008214}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775033926661,"responseId":"msg_c68a0ddb-77a8-41be-aae9-c9ae8f77e4ea"}}
