{"type":"message","id":"d661c27e","parentId":"a682e5b0","timestamp":"2026-04-01T10:11:54.362Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问我这次升级都改了哪些配置。让我回顾一下我们今天所做的所有配置更改：\n\n1. 添加了 memorySearch 配置到 agents.defaults 中\n2. 添加了 openai provider 到 models.providers 中，指向 DashScope\n3. 在 openai provider 中配置了 apiKey\n\n让我总结一下所有的配置更改。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]\n## 本次配置修改总结\n\n### 1. 添加 `memorySearch` 配置\n**位置：** `agents.defaults.memorySearch`\n\n```json\n\"memorySearch\": {\n  \"sources\": [\"memory\"],\n  \"provider\": \"openai\",\n  \"model\": \"text-embedding-v3\"\n}\n```\n\n### 2. 添加 OpenAI Provider 配置\n**位置：** `models.providers.openai`\n\n```json\n\"openai\": {\n  \"baseUrl\": \"https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/compatible-mode/v1\",\n  \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n  \"apiKey\": \"sk-a2675c4123764e46880426a87bff42de\",\n  \"models\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"text-embedding-v3\",\n      \"name\": \"Qwen Text Embedding V3\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 修改的文件\n**仅修改了：** `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n\n---\n\n## 效果\n✅ 向量检索已启用  \n✅ 使用阿里云千问 `text-embedding-v3` 模型  \n✅ 所有工作空间索引完成  \n✅ Vector: ready (1024 维度)\n\n---\n\n## 未完成的事\n1. **飞书 CLI 认证** - 需要点浏览器链接\n2. **GitHub 技能安装** - clawhub 限流，稍后再试\n3. **飞书日历创建日程** - 等认证完成后\n\n还有其他要弄的吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":435,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":102247,"totalTokens":102688,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.0001218,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00012246000000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775038302956,"responseId":"msg_b333fee1-2bf9-4968-bb98-0c4c42020de1"}}
